@page "/profile"

<PageTitle>Ibasho - プロフィール</PageTitle>

<div class="space-y-4 px-4">
    <div class="mt-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div>
            <img class="h-32 w-full object-cover" src="https://placehold.co/600x200/BFDBFE/3B82F6?text=Banner" alt="Profile banner">
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
            <div class="flex items-end -mt-16">
                <img class="h-24 w-24 rounded-full border-4 border-white" src="https://placehold.co/150x150/93C5FD/FFFFFF?text=Me" alt="My Avatar">
                <button onclick="event.preventDefault(); location.href = '/profile/edit';" class="ml-auto px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold border border-gray-300 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100">プロフィールを編集</button>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">自分</h2>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">@("@me")</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">こんにちは！これはプロフィールの自己紹介文です。Ibashoアプリを作成しています。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex mt-4 space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <p class="cursor-pointer" onclick="showContent('follow-list')"><span class="font-bold text-gray-800">120</span> フォロー中</p>
                <p class="cursor-pointer" onclick="showContent('follow-list')"><span class="font-bold text-gray-800">85</span> フォロワー</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-200">
            <nav class="flex">
                <a href="#" id="profile-tab-posts" onclick="event.preventDefault(); switchProfileTab('posts')" class="flex-1 text-center py-3 font-medium text-sky-500 border-b-2 border-sky-500">投稿</a>
                <a href="#" id="profile-tab-likes" onclick="event.preventDefault(); switchProfileTab('likes')" class="flex-1 text-center py-3 font-medium text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-100">いいね</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="profile-content-posts" class="space-y-4">
        <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="https://placehold.co/150x150/93C5FD/FFFFFF?text=Me" alt="My Avatar">
                <div class="flex-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                        <span class="font-bold">自分</span>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">@("@me") · 2日前</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-1">プロフィール画面を作成中。いい感じにできたかな？</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="profile-content-likes" class="hidden space-y-4">
        <div class="p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">あなたが「いいね」しました</p>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full cursor-pointer" onclick="showContent('user-profile')" src="https://placehold.co/100x100/E2E8F0/4A5568?text=User" alt="User Avatar">
                <div class="flex-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                        <span class="font-bold">ユーザー名１</span>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">@("@user1") · 5分前</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-1">Tailwind CSSを使ってSNSのUIを作るの、楽しい！ライトブルーがいい感じ。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>